---
// Componente About con diseño UX moderno
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white relative">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
		<!-- Header de sección -->


			<!-- Contenido principal -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
				<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
				</svg>
				About me
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
				Building digital experiences with 
				<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">passion & precision</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				I believe great software combines technical excellence with intuitive design. 
				Here's what drives my development process.
			</p>
		</div>
			
		<!-- Education & Growth -->
		<div class="mt-16 mb-16 relative">
			<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 via-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-3xl p-1 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/20">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-[1.35rem] p-8 lg:p-10">
					<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
						<!-- Icon & Title -->
						<div class="flex-shrink-0">
							<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30">
								<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"></path>
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"></path>
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<!-- Content -->
						<div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Education & Self-Growth</h3>
								<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-indigo-600 font-medium">
									<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
									</svg>
									<a href="https://www.davinci.edu.ar/" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">
										DaVinci University — Buenos Aires, Argentina
									</a>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								With over <span class="font-semibold text-indigo-600">2 years</span> into my Systems Analyst degree, 
								I've built a solid foundation in software architecture, databases, full stack development, 
								<span class="font-medium text-slate-800">process documentation & diagrams</span>, 
								<span class="font-medium text-slate-800">requirements engineering</span>, and 
								<span class="font-medium text-slate-800">agile methodologies</span>. 
								But my learning doesn't stop at the classroom.
							</p>
							
							<!-- GPA Badge 
							<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 border-2 border-amber-300 rounded-2xl px-5 py-3 shadow-lg shadow-amber-100/50 animate-pulse-slow">
								<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
									<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
										<path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<div class="text-xs font-medium text-amber-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Current GPA</div>
									<div class="text-2xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-yellow-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">9.26 <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-500">/ 10</span></div>
								</div>
							</div>
							-->
							<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-2">
								<div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
									<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
										<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Self-Driven Learner</div>
										<div class="text-xs text-slate-600">Exploring new languages & sharpening skills in my free time</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
									<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
										<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Ahead of the Curve</div>
										<div class="text-xs text-slate-600">Proactively studying advanced topics beyond the syllabus</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
									<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
										<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Dev-Focused English</div>
										<div class="text-xs text-slate-600">Practicing technical English for global collaboration</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>





	
		
		<!-- Grid principal -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
			<!-- Stack tecnológico -->
			<div class="space-y-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/50 relative overflow-hidden">
				<!-- Elemento decorativo -->
				<div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-100 rounded-full opacity-60 blur-2xl"></div>
				<div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-20 h-20 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full opacity-60 blur-2xl"></div>
				
				<div class="relative z-10">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
							</svg>
						</div>
						Technology Stack
					</h3>
					
					<!-- Conocimientos Principales -->
					<div class="mb-8">
						<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
							Main Skills
						</h4>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
							<div class="group p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-green-50 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100 hover:border-green-200">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
										<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path d="M8.851 18.56s-.917.534.653.714c1.902.218 2.874.187 4.969-.211 0 0 .552.346 1.321.646-4.699 2.013-10.633-.118-6.943-1.149M8.276 15.933s-1.028.761.542.924c2.032.209 3.636.227 6.413-.308 0 0 .384.389.987.602-5.679 1.661-12.007.13-7.942-1.218M13.116 11.475c1.158 1.333-.304 2.533-.304 2.533s2.939-1.518 1.589-3.418c-1.261-1.772-2.228-2.652 3.007-5.688 0-.001-8.216 2.051-4.292 6.573M19.33 20.504s.679.559-.747.991c-2.712.822-11.288 1.069-13.669.033-.856-.373.75-.89 1.254-.998.527-.114.828-.093.828-.093-.953-.671-6.156 1.317-2.643 1.887 9.58 1.553 17.462-.7 14.977-1.82M9.292 13.21s-4.362 1.036-1.544 1.412c1.189.159 3.561.123 5.77-.062 1.806-.152 3.618-.477 3.618-.477s-.637.272-1.098.587c-4.429 1.165-12.986.623-10.522-.568 2.082-1.006 3.776-.892 3.776-.892M17.116 17.584c4.503-2.34 2.421-4.589.968-4.285-.355.074-.515.138-.515.138s.132-.207.385-.297c2.875-1.011 5.086 2.981-.928 4.562 0-.001.07-.062.09-.118M14.401 0s2.494 2.494-2.365 6.33c-3.896 3.077-.888 4.832-.001 6.836-2.274-2.053-3.943-3.858-2.824-5.539 1.644-2.469 6.197-3.665 5.19-7.627M9.734 23.924c4.322.277 10.959-.153 11.116-2.198 0 0-.302.775-3.572 1.391-3.688.694-8.239.613-10.937.168 0-.001.553.457 3.393.639"/>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Java</div>
										<div class="text-sm text-slate-600">OOP • Spring</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<div class="group p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-green-50 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100 hover:border-green-200">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
										<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
											<path d="M1.5 0h21l-1.91 21.563L11.977 24l-8.564-2.438L1.5 0zm7.031 9.75l-.232-2.718 10.059.003.23-2.622L5.412 4.41l.698 8.01h9.126l-.326 3.426-2.91.804-2.955-.81-.188-2.11H6.248l.33 4.171L12 19.351l5.379-1.443.744-8.157H8.531z"/>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">HTML/CSS</div>
										<div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Responsive • Modern</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<div class="group p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-green-50 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 border border-slate-100 hover:border-green-200">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
